### 판매자 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/seller/signUp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "seller1@example.com",
  "username": "seller1",
  "password": "seller1-password"
}

### 판매자 접근 토큰 발행
POST http://localhost:8080/seller/issueToken
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "seller1@example.com",
  "password": "seller1-password"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### 판매자 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/seller/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 판매자 상품 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/seller/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


{
  "name": "Product 2",
  "imageUri": "http://example.com/product2.jpg",
  "description": "Product 2 description",
  "priceAmount": 2000,
  "stockQuantity": 20
}

> {%
  client.global.set("location", response.headers.valueOf("Location"));
%}

### 판매자 상품 조회
GET http://localhost:8080{{location}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 판매자 상품 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/seller/products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
